This article mainly aims at the pattern dynamics generated by means of an SI model. In Sect. 2, we describe an SI model. In Sect. 3, we analyze the bifurcation and get the Turing bifurcation under the critical condition. Furthermore, we apply nonlinear multi-scale analysis to gain amplitude equation and obtain different types of Turing pattern. Finally, some conclusions are given.

